{
  "texts": [
    "Internal and external factors influence digital transformation in small and mediumsized enterprises (SMEs).",
    "Organizational strategy is essential on the inside, helping small and medium-sized enterprises (SMEs) overcome obstacles by maximizing strengths and adjusting to new circumstances in the ever-changing digital landscape.",
    "Information technology (IT) capabilities are pivotal, requiring strategic investments in research and development to fortify technological foundations.",
    "A technologyfocused philosophy and flexible organizational structures are also crucial to a successful digital transformation within an organization.",
    "Government policies and regulations have an outwardly significant effect on digital transformation because they provide direction and incentives."
  ]
}